<comment id="12017" author="712020:8c1c869b-c4be-4401-b6c0-3f69c6178d55" created="Fri, 10 Apr 2026 13:31:04 +0900"><ul> <li>The doc says “top ONE best-fit TTS voice models” and also says output is an array of recommendations. Should the orchestrator return exactly one item or multiple ranked options?</li> <li>The available voice pool in docs does not match the current MVP page catalog. Which list is canonical?</li> <li>Is recommendation based only on character DNA, or also on guide info / script / language?</li> <li>If the recommended voice is filtered out by gender/style toggles, should it still be pinned at top or disappear with the filter?</li> <li>Persistence scope is unclear: selected voice saved per guide, per POI, per language, or all three?</li> </ul> </comment>
<comment id="12062" author="712020:8c1c869b-c4be-4401-b6c0-3f69c6178d55" created="Sat, 11 Apr 2026 23:07:01 +0900"><p>從工程角度，我會建議再補 4 個點，這樣前後端比較不會各自解讀。</p> <p><b>主要建議</b></p> <ol> <li><b>Recommendation response contract 仍有矛盾</b><br/> 現在文字同時出現： <ul> <li><tt>top ONE best-fit</tt></li> <li><tt>Select the ONE most appropriate</tt></li> <li>但 Expected Output 又寫成 <tt>an array called recommendations</tt></li> </ul> </li> </ol> <p>這會讓工程端不確定要不要做 list。<br/> 建議二選一：</p> <ul> <li>如果真的只要一個：</li> </ul> <p>{{</p> { "recommended_voice_id": "Aoede", "match_reason": "..." } <p>}}</p> <ul> <li>如果保留 array：<br/> 明寫 <tt>recommendations</tt> 必須 <b>exactly 1 item</b></li> </ul> <ol> <li><b>「persisted to the backend item payload」要補 scope</b><br/> 這句還不夠精確。要補清楚是綁定到哪個層級： <ul> <li>per guide</li> <li>per POI/item</li> <li>per language</li> <li>per generation run</li> </ul> </li> </ol> <p>我建議至少明寫：</p> <ul> <li>Creator 最終選定 voice 是存在哪個 entity</li> <li>後續 audio generation 讀哪一份設定作為 source of truth</li> </ul> <ol> <li><tt>character_personality</tt> <b>建議改成明確欄位集合</b><br/> 現在寫： <ul> <li><tt>Character Profile: {{character_personality</tt>}}</li> <li><tt>mapped to character DNA</tt></li> </ul> </li> </ol> <p>但工程端還是不知道實際要塞哪些欄位。<br/> 建議直接改成類似：</p> <ul> <li><tt>character_profile.role_label</tt></li> <li><tt>character_profile.personality_dna</tt></li> <li><tt>character_profile.linguistic_fingerprint</tt></li> <li>optional <tt>character_profile.timbre_hint</tt></li> </ul> <p>這樣 prompt builder 和 <span class="jira-issue-macro" data-jira-key="LS-88" > <a href="https://laxy.atlassian.net/browse/LS-88" class="jira-issue-macro-key issue-link" title="7.2 Character Library (n5_character_select)" > <img class="icon" src="https://laxy.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10315?size=medium" /> LS-88 </a> <span class="aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle aui-lozenge-complete jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">To Do</span> </span> schema 就能對齊。</p> <ol> <li><b>Voice source of truth 建議寫死一個</b><br/> 現在 ticket 內有 voice list，另外 style 又參照 Confluence。<br/> 這樣可以，但最好補一句： <ul> <li>voice IDs 以此 ticket / System Architecture <tt>Available Voice Models</tt> 為 canonical source</li> <li>style description 僅作 UI 展示與 recommendation context，不代表 TTS API 的硬參數</li> </ul> </li> </ol> <p>這樣比較不會讓人誤會 <tt>Breezy / Gravelly / Middle pitch</tt> 是直接送給模型的固定欄位。</p> <p><b>次要建議</b></p> <ul> <li><tt>Select the ONE most appropriate voices</tt> 這句文法建議改成 <tt>voice</tt></li> <li><tt>Voice option as following</tt> 建議改成 <tt>Available voice options are as follows</tt></li> <li>Acceptance Criteria 的 <tt>exactly ONE voice IDs</tt> 建議改成 <tt>exactly ONE voice ID</tt></li> </ul> <p><b>我會建議補進 story 的一句話</b><br/> 可以直接加：</p> <p><tt>The recommendation service must return exactly one valid voice ID from the configured Available Voice Models list. If parsing fails or the returned ID is outside the allowed pool, the system must surface a recoverable error and not persist the result.</tt></p></comment>
